title: Flappy Bird GX2
author: rw-r-r_0644
description: A Flappy Bird clone for Wii U
details:
A Flappy Bird clone for WiiU using GX2 graphics
  Don't hit pipes!
  And don't fall down too!
  
  Press A to start and jump
